metadata.name: Heavenly Eden
metadata.description:
As she inhaled the earthy fragrance of petrichor, a sense of serenity washed over the woman. In this galactic paradise, her garden was her safe haven, a place of solace amidst the tumultuous universe. Amidst the vibrant flora and fauna, she found a sense of calm that she never could elsewhere.

Collaboration by Ponse Lakiva & Eli Leno
